OL,3,CJob rejections left man with sight
OL,4,Cproblems feeling 'on the scrapheap'
OL,6,FA man with a visual impairment from
OL,7,FCastle Cary says he felt he was 'on
OL,8,Fthe scrapheap' after being
OL,9,Fconsistently turned down for jobs.
OL,11,FMark Catton says he was even let go
OL,12,Fjust weeks into a role, with his boss
OL,13,Fsaying he was worried about him having
OL,14,Fan accident because of his sight.
OL,16,FMark eventually came across a
OL,17,Fgovernment programme called SWAP,
OL,18,Fwhich led to him finally getting a job
OL,19,Fat the NHS in Somerset.
