OL,3,CJob rejections left man with sight
OL,4,Cproblems feeling 'on the scrapheap'
OL,6,FMark, 60, had been out of work since
OL,7,Fbeing made redundant during the Covid-
OL,8,F19 pandemic over four years ago. He
OL,9,Fsaid the job application process
OL,10,Fshattered his confidence.
OL,12,FMark has Retinitis Pigmentosa, a
OL,13,Fcondition where cells in the retina
OL,14,Fdie which leads to sight loss. As a
OL,15,Fresult, Mark has faced difficulty
OL,16,Fapplying for work, adding he felt his
OL,17,Fage and condition meant some employers
OL,18,Fdid not want to take the chance on him.
