OL,3,CJob rejections left man with sight
OL,4,Cproblems feeling 'on the scrapheap'
OL,6,FHowever, after turning to his local
OL,7,FJobcentre he was signed up to a Sector-
OL,8,Fbased Workplace Academy Programme
OL,9,F(SWAP) and within weeks, Mark was
OL,10,Foffered his job at Yeovil Hospital.
OL,12,FSWAP helps tackle unemployment in key
OL,13,Fsectors through work experience,
OL,14,Fcoaching and intensive interview
OL,15,Fsupport.
