OL,3,CJob rejections left man with sight
OL,4,Cproblems feeling 'on the scrapheap'
OL,6,FJoining in November 2023, Mark settled
OL,7,Fin well as an estates administrator
OL,8,Fwhere he, and his guide dog Nathan,
OL,9,Fsupport the smooth running of the
OL,10,Fhospital ` from answering requests for
OL,11,Frepairs, security and document filing.
OL,13,FMark said: "I feel so privileged to
OL,14,Fhave got this job for so many reasons.
OL,15,FMy life has been changed so very much
OL,16,Fand all in such an unbelievable way `
OL,17,FI'm now enjoying life and work.
