OL,3,CJob rejections left man with sight
OL,4,Cproblems feeling 'on the scrapheap'
OL,6,F"This has been such a big change in my
OL,7,Flife, from being way down there on the
OL,8,Fscrapheap to seeing this opportunity
OL,9,Fopening up.
OL,11,F"I'm so thankful to my colleagues for
OL,12,Fbeing so supportive. I'm loving life
OL,13,Fto the fullest and want to say a huge
OL,14,Fthank you to the SWAP team for turning
OL,15,Fmy life around"
