OL,4,Cproblems feeling 'on the scrapheap'
OL,6,FMinister for Disabled People, Health
OL,7,Fand Work, Mims Davies MP, said:
OL,8,F"Mark's story is incredibly inspiring
OL,9,Fand to see how the support of his work
OL,10,Fcoaches and colleagues has given him a
OL,11,Fchance to shine in a new role is
OL,12,Famazing.
OL,14,F"We know there are thousands of people
OL,15,Fout there, like Mark, who want to work
OL,16,Fbut need a bit of support, and we, at
OL,17,Fthe Department for Work and Pensions,
OL,18,Fare here to help.
