OL,3,CJob rejections left man with sight
OL,4,Cproblems feeling 'on the scrapheap'
OL,6,F"I wish Mark, and Nathan, all the best
OL,7,Fin their new role and encourage others
OL,8,Fto tap into the support and expertise
OL,9,Favailable in our Jobcentres."
OL,11,FAnna Taylor, future workforce project
OL,12,Fcoordinator at Somerset NHS Foundation
OL,13,FTrust, said: "Seeing the way the SWAP
OL,14,Fhas transformed Mark's life, not just
OL,15,Fin finding him a career, but also
OL,16,Fhelping him to regain his confidence
OL,17,Fand sense of purpose, has been
OL,18,Ffantastic to see.
